  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseDrone_GDClone">
    <defName>Drone_ArchoHunter</defName>
    <label>trick mine drone</label>
    <description>Replicas of archotech trick mine after being reverse-analyzed by the black-clad mechanoids, responsible for replacing their combatants to carry out regular defense and patrol tasks. \n\nIn the patrol state, this drone will randomly teleport at a certain frequency. When a moving target is detected, it will enter an alert state. Keeping still can relieve its alertness. After determining the target, it will quickly approach and self-destruct.</description>
